hadiths[111]{hadithnumber,text}:
2304,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya : ''do nematein aisi hain jin mein aksar log apna nuqsan kartey hain''. eik tandurusti aur dusri faraaghat
2305,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kon aisa shakhs hai jo mujh sey in kalmaat ko sun kar un par amal karey ya aisey shakhs ko sikhlaey jo un par amal kerey'', Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool! main aisa karunga, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney in paanch baaton ko gin kar bataya : ''tum haram chizon sey bacho, sab logon sey ziyada abid ho jaaogey aur Allah Taala ki taqseem shuda rizq par razi raho, sab logon sey ziyada be niaz rahogey, aur apney padosi key sath ehsan karo pakkey sachey momin rahogey. aur dusron key liye wohi pasand karo jo apney liye pasand kartey ho sachey musalman ho jaaogey aur ziyada na hanso isliye ke ziyada hansna dil ko murda kar deta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Jaafar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Hasan Basri ka samaa, Abu-Hurera sey Sabit nahin, 3- isi tarah Ayub , Yunus bin Ubaid aur Ali bin Zaid sey marvi hai un sab ka kehna hai ke Hasan Basri ney Abu-Hurera sey nahin suna hai, 4- abu-Ubaida naaji ney isey Hasan Basri sey riwayat kartey huye is ko Hasan Basri ka qol kaha hai aur ye nahin zikr kya ke ye hadees Hasan Basri Abu-Hurera sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Abu-Hurera Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
2306,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' saat chizon sey pehley nek aamal karney mein jaldi karo, tumhen aisey faqr ka intizar hai jo sab kuch bhula dalney wala hai? ya aisi maldari ka jo tughyani paida karney wali hai? ya aisi bimari ka jo mufsid hai (yani itaat Ilaahi mein khalal dalney wali) hai? ya aisey budhapey ka jo aql ko kho deney wala hai? ya aisi maut ka jo jaldi hi aaney wali hai? ya us dajjaal ka intizar hai jis ka intizar sab sey burey ghaayab ka intizar hai? ya us qiyamat ka jo qiyamat nihayat sakht aur kadwi hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Aaraj Abu-Hurera sey marvi hadees hum sirf Muharriz bin Harun ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- Bishr bin umr aur unkey ilawa logon ney bhi isey Muharriz bin Harun sey riwayat kya hai, 4- Maamar ney eik aisey shakhs sey suna hai jisney b-sanad (سعيدا المقبري an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai is mein « هل تنتظرون » ki bajaey « تنتظرون » hai."
2307,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''lazzaton ko todney wali) yani maut ( ko kasrat sey yad kya karo '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib , padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2308,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) jab kisi qabristaan par thehertey to itna rotey ke aap ki dadhi tar ho jati , un sey kisi ney kaha ke jab aap key samney jannat o jahannam ka zikr kya jata hai to nahin rotey hain aur qabr ko dekh kar is qadr ro rahey hain? to kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya hai : '' aakhirat key manaazil mein sey qabr pehli manzil hai, so agar kisi ney qabr key azab sey najat pai to uskey baad key marhaley aasan hongey aur agar jisey azabe-qabr sey najat na mil saki to uskey baad key manaazil sakht tar hongi'' , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney mazeed kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya : '' ghabrahat aur sakhti key aetbar sey qabr ki tarah kisi aur manzar ko nahin dekha '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf Hisham bin Yusuf ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2309,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milna chahega to Allah Taala bhi us sey milna chahega , aur jo Allah Taala sey milna napasand karey to Allah Taala bhi us sey milna napasand kerega '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada ki hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ummul-momenin Aaisha , Anas aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2310,"jab ye aayate-kareema : « وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين » nazil hui to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya : '' aey abdul-Muttalib ki beti Safiya!, aey Muhammad ki beti Fatima ! aey abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! Allah ki taraf sey tum logon key nafa o nuqsan ka mujhey kuch bhi ikhtiyar nahin hai, tum merey maal mein sey tum sab ko jo kuch maangna ho wo mujh sey mang lo padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- un mein sey baaz ney isi tarah Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat ki hai, aur baaz ney « an Hisham an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey mursalan riwayat ki hai aur « an Aaeysha» ka zikr nahin kya, 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2311,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key khof aur dar sey roney wala shakhs jahannam mein nahin ja sakta jab tak ke doodh than mein wapis na pahunch jaey aur Allah ki raah ka gard o ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan dono ikhatta nahin ho saktey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Rehana aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman aal Talha key azad karda ghulam hain madni hain, Suqa hain, un sey Shoba aur Sufiyan Sory ney riwayat ki hai."
2312,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' beshak main wo chiz dekh raha hun jo tum nahin dekhtey aur wo sun raha hun jo tum nahin suntey. beshak aasman charchara raha hai aur usey charcharaney ka haq bhi hai, isliye ke is mein chaar ungal ki bhi jagah nahin khaali hai magar koi na koi farishta apni peshani Allah key huzur rakhey huye hai, Allah ki qism ! jo main janta hun agar wo tum log bhi jaan lo to hansogey kam aur roogey ziyada aur bistaron par apni aurton sey lutf andoz na hogey, aur yaqinan tum log Allah Taala sey fariyad kartey huye maidaanon mein nikal jatey'' , (aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu)) farmaya kartey they ke '' kaash! main eik darkht hota jo kaat diya jata ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- iskey alawa eik dusri sanad sey bhi marvi hai ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : ''kash main eik darkht hota ke jisey log kaat daltey'' , padhi. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , ibne-Abbas aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2313,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo main janta hun agar tum log jaan letey to hanstey kam aur rotey ziyada ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2314,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi kabhi aisi baat keh deta hai jis mein wo khud koi harj nahin samajhta halanke uski wajeh sey wo sattar baras tak jahannam ki aag mein girta chala jaeyga'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2315,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' tabahi o barbadi hai us shakhs key liye jo aisi baat kehta hai ke log sun kar hansen halanke wo baat jhooti hoti hai to aisey shakhs key liye tabahi hi tabahi hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2316,"eik Sabab ki wafat ho gaee , eik aadmi ney kaha : tujhey jannat ki basharat ho, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' shayad tumhen nahin malum ke usney koi aisi baat kahi ho jo be-faeyda ho, ya aisi chiz key sath bukhl sey kaam liya ho jiskey kharch karney sey uska kuch nuqsan na hota ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
2317,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi shakhs key Islam ki khoobi ye hai ke wo la-yaani aur fuzul baaton ko chhod dey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum is hadees ko abu-Salma ki riwayat sey jisey wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2318,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aadmi key Islam ki khoobi ye hai ke wo aisi chizon ko chhod dey jo us sey ghair mutalliq hon''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zohri key shagirdon mein sey kaee logon ney isi tarah (عن الزهري an علي بن حسين an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey Malik ki hadees ki tarah mursalan riwayat ki hai, 2- hamarey nazdik ye hadees abu-Salma ki Abu-Hurera sey marvi hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, 3- Ali bin Husain (Zenul-Aabedin) ki mulaqat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey Sabit nahin hai."
2319,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' tum mein sey koi Allah ki raza-mandi ki aisi baat kehta hai jis key barey mein wo nahin janta ke uski wajeh sey uska martaba kahan tak pahunchega halanke Allah Taala uski is baat ki wajeh sey uskey haq mein us din tak key liye apni khushnoodi aur raza-mandi likh deta hai jis din wo us sey milega , aur tum mein sey koi Allah Taala ki narazagi ki aisi baat kehta hai jis key barey mein usey guman bhi nahin hota ke uski wajeh sey uska wabal kahan tak pahunchega jabke Allah uski is baat ki wajeh sey uskey haq mein us din tak key liye hai jis din wo us sey milega apni narazagi likh deta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur isey isi tarah sey kaee logon ney Muhammad bin Amr sey usi key misl riwayat kya hai yani (عن محمد بن عمرو an أبيه an جده an بلال بن الحارث) ki sanad sey , 3- is hadees ko Malik ney (عن محمد بن عمرو an أبيه an بلال بن الحارث) ki sanad sey riwayat kya hai lekin is mein « an Abeeh » ka zikr nahin hai, 4- is bab mein Umme-Habiba sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2320,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key nazdik duniya ki waqat agar eik machar key par key barabar bhi hoti to wo kisi kafir ko is mein sey eik ghoont pani bhi na pilata''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2321,"main bhi un sawaron key sath tha jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik bakri key marey huye bachey key paas khadey they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya tum log isey dekh rahey ho ke jab ye iskey malikon key nazdik haqeer aur be qeemat ho gaya'' to unhoney usey phenk diya, Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! iskey be-qeemat honey ki buniyad hi par logon ney isey phenk diya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''duniya Allah Taala key nazdik issey bhi ziyada haqeer aur be waqat hai jitna ye apney logon key nazdik haqeer aur be waqat hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2322,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''beshak duniya maloon hai aur jo kuch duniya mein hai wo bhi maloon hai, siwaye Allah ki yad aur us chiz key jis ko Allah pasand karta hai, ya aalim (ilm waley) aur mutaallim (ilm seekhney waley) key '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2323,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''duniya ki misal aakhirat key samney aisi hai jaisey tum mein sey koi shakhs apni ungli samandar mein duboey aur phir dekhey ke uski ungli samandar ka kitna pani apney sath laee hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ismail bin abi Khalid ki kunniyat abu-Adbullah hai, 3- Qais key walid abu-Haazim ka naam abd bin Auf hai aur ye Sabab hain."
2324,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' duniya momin key liye qaid khana ( jail ( hai aur kafir key liye jannat ( baagh o bahar ( hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2325,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''main teen baaton par qism khata hun aur main tum logon sey eik baat bayan kar raha hun jisey yad rakho '' , '' kisi bandey key maal mein sadqa deney sey koi kami nahin aati ( ye pehli baat hai) , aur kisi bandey par kisi qism ka zulm ho aur is par wo sabr karey to Allah uski izzat ko badha deta hai) dusri baat hai) , aur agar koi shakhs mangney key liye sawal ka darwaza kholta hai to Allah uskey liye faqr o mohtaji ka darwaza khol deta hai ''. (ya usi key hum maana aap ney koi aur kalma kaha ( ) ye teesri baat hai) aur tum logon sey eik aur baat bayan kar raha hun isey bhi achi tarah yad rakho : '' ye duniya chaar qism key logon key liye hai : eik banda wo hai jisey Allah ney maal aur ilm ki dolat di, wo apney rab sey us maal key kamaaney aur kharch karney mein darta hai aur us maal key zariey sila rehmi karta hai padhi. aur is mein sey Allah key huquq ki adaegi ka bhi khayal rakhta hai padhi. aisey bandey ka darja sab darjon sey behtar hai. aur eik wo banda hai jisey Allah ney ilm diya, lekin maal o dolat sey usey mehroom rakha phir bhi uski niyat sachi hai aur wo kehta hai ke kaash! merey paas bhi maal hota to main us shakhs ki tarah amal karta lihaza usey uski sachi niyat ki wajeh sey pehley shakhs ki tarah ajr barabar milega, aur eik wo banda hai jisey Allah ney maal o dolat sey nawaza lekin usey ilm sey mehroom rakha wo apney maal mein ghalat rawish ikhtiyar karta hai, us maal key kamaaney aur kharch karney mein apney rab sey nahin darta hai, na hi sila rehmi karta hai aur na hi us maal mein Allah key haq ka khayal rakhta hai to aisey shakhs ka darja sab darjon sey badtar hai, aur eik wo banda hai jisey Allah ney maal o dolat aur ilm dono sey mehroom rakha , wo kehta hai kaash! merey paas maal hota to falan ki tarah mein bhi amal karta ( yani : burey kamon mein maal kharch karta ( to uski niyat ka wabal usey milega aur dono ka azab aur baare-gunah barabar hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2326,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs faaqey ka shikar ho aur is par sabr na karkey logon sey bayan karta phirey padhi. to uska faaqa khatam nahin hoga, aur jo faaqey ka shikar ho aur usey Allah key hawaley kar key is par sabr sey kaam ley to qarib hai ke Allah Taala usey der ya sawer rozi dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2327,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) abu-Hashim bin Utba bin Rabeea al-Qarshi ki bimari key waqt unki iyaadat key liye aaye aur kaha : aey mamu jaan ! kya chiz aap ko rulaa rahi hai? kisi dard sey aap be chain hain ya duniya ki hirs sata rahi hai, abu-Hashim ney kaha : aisi koi baat nahin hai, albatta Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey eik wasiyat ki thi jis par mein amal na kar saka . aap ney farmaya tha : '' tumharey liye purey sarmaye mein sey eik khaadim aur eik sawari jo Allah ki raah mein kaam aaye kafi hai, jabke is waqt mainey apney paas bahut kuch jama kar liya hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- zyada aur Ubeda bin Humed ney (عن منصور an أبي Waeyl an سمرة بن سهم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai jis mein ye naqal kya hai ke Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) abu-Hashim key paas dakhil huye phir usi key maanind hadees zikr ki padhi. 2- is bab mein Barida Aslami ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya hai."
2328,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jaaidaad padhi. ko mat banao ke uski wajeh sey tumhen duniya ki raghbat ho jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2329,"eik Erabi (dehati) ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! logon mein sab sey behtar shakhs kon hai? aap ney farmaya : '' jiski umr lambi ho aur amal nek ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2330,"eik shakhs ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! logon mein sab sey behtar shakhs kon hai? aap ney farmaya : '' jiski umr lambi ho aur amal nek ho '' , us aadmi ney phir puchha ke logon mein sab sey badtar shakhs kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jis ki umr lambi ho aur amal bura ho'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2331,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat key aksar logon ki umr saath sey sattar saal tak key darmiyan hogi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Saaleh ki ye hadees jisey wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey uskey ilawa kaee aur sanadon sey bhi marvi hai."
2332,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat nahin qaaim hogi yahan tak ke zamana qarib ho jaeyga padhi. saal eik mahina key barabar ho jaeyga jabke eik mahina eik haftey key barabar aur eik hafta eik din key barabar aur eik din eik sa'at ( ghadi ( key barabar ho jaeyga aur eik sa'at ( ghadi ( aag sey paida honey wali chingari key barabar ho jaeygi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey ye hadees gharib hai.
2333,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey badan key baaz hissey ko pakad kar farmaya : '' tum duniya mein aisey raho goya tum eik musafir ya raahgeer ho, aur apna shumar qabr walon mein karo''. Mujahid kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney mujh sey kaha : jab tum subh karo to Sham ka yaqin mat rakho aur jab Sham karo to subh ka yaqin na rakho, aur bimari sey qabl sehat o tandurusti ki haalat mein aur maut sey qabl zindagi ki haalat mein kuch kar lo isliye ke Allah key banday! tumhen nahin malum ke kal tumhara naam kya hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Aamash ney Mujahid sey , Mujahid ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey is hadees ki isi tarah sey riwayat ki hai."
2334,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ye ibne-Adam hai aur ye uski maut hai'', aur aap ney apna haath apni guddi par rakha phir usey daraz kya aur farmaya : ''ye uski ummid hai, ye uski ummid hai, ye uski ummid hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2335,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey paas sey guzrey, hum apna chhappar ka makaan durust kar rahey they, aap ney puchha : ye kya hai? hamney arz kya ke ye ghar bosida ho chuka hai, lihaza hum isko theek kar rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''main to mamley ( maut ( ko is sey bhi ziyada qarib dekh raha hun '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2336,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : '' har ummat ki aazmaaish kisi na kisi chiz mein hai aur meri ummat ki aazmaaish maal mein hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum Muawiya bin Saleh ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain."
2337,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar aadmi key paas soney ki do waadiyaan hon to usey eik teesri wadi ki khahish hogi aur uska pet kisi chiz sey nahin bharega siwaye mitti sey . aur Allah Taala har us shakhs ki tauba qubul karta hai jo us sey tauba karey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab, abu Saeed Khudri, Aaisha, ibn Zuber , abu Waqid , Jabir , ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2338,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''do chizon ki mohabbat mein boodhey ka dil jawan rehta hai : lambi zindagi ki mohabbat, doosrey maal ki mohabbat''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2339,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aadmi boodha ho jata hai albatta uskey andar do cheezen jawan rehti hain eik ( lambi ( zindagi ki khahish , doosrey maal ki hirs ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2340,"Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''duniya ka ye matlab nahin hai ke aadmi halal chiz ko apney ooper haram kar ley aur maal ko barbad kar dey balke iska matlab ye hai ke jo maal tumharey haath mein hai, is par tum ko us maal sey ziyada bharosa na ho jo Allah key haath mein hai aur tumhen musibat key sawab ki is qadr raghbat (dilchaspi) ho ke jab tum musibat mein giraftar ho jaao to khahish karo ke ye musibat baqi rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Raavi hadees Amr bin Waqid hadees ke munkir hai."
2341,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''duniya ki chizon mein sey ibne-Adam ka haq siwaye uskey aur kuchh nahin ke uskey liye eik ghar ho jis mein wo zindagi basar kar sakey aur itna kapda ho jis sey wo apna sattar dhanp sakey, aur roti aur pani key liye bartan hon jin sey wo khaney peeney ka jatan kar sakey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Hurriyat bin Saaib ki riwayat sey hai. 2- mainey abu-Daawood Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Salam Balkhi ko ye kehtey huye suna ke Nazar bin Shumeil ney kaha : « جلف الخبز » ka matlab hai wo roti jis key sath salan na ho."
2342,"wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein pahunchey aur aap « ألهاكم التكاثر » ki tilawat kar rahey they to aap ney farmaya : ''ibne-Adam kehta hai ke mera maal , mera maal , halanke tumhara maal sirf wo hai jo tum ney sadqa kar diya aur usey aagey chala diya, aur khaya aur usey khatam kar diya ya pehna aur usey puraanaa kar diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2343,"Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ibne-Adam ! agar to apni hajat sey zayed maal Allah ki raah mein kharch kerega to ye terey liye behtar hoga, aur agar to usey rok rakheyga to ye terey liye bura hoga, aur ba-qadr kharch karney mein teri malamat nahin ki jaeygi aur sadqa aur khairat detey waqt un logon sey shuru kar jinki kafalat terey zimme hai, aur ooper wala (deney wala) haath nichey waley haath (maangney waley) sey behtar hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2344,"Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar tum log Allah par tawakkul ( bharosa ( karo jaisa ke is par tawakkul ( bharosa ( karney ka haq hai to tumhen isi tarah rizq milega jaisa ke parindon ko milta hai ke subah ko wo bhookey nikaltey hain aur Sham ko aasooda (bhare pet) wapis aatey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2345,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein do bhai they, un main eik Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein rehta tha aur doosra mehnat aur mazduri karta tha, mehnat aur mazduri karney waley ney eik martaba Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey apney bhai ki shikayat ki to aap ney farmaya : ''shayad tujhey usi ki wajeh sey rozi milti ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2346,"Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey jisney bhi subah ki is haal mein ke wo apney ghar ya qom mein aman sey ho aur jismani lihaz sey bilkul tandurust ho aur din bhar ki rozi uskey paas mojud ho to goya uskey liye puri duniya samet di gaee.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf Marwan bin Muawiya hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- aur « حيزت » ka matlab ye hai ke jama ki gaee."
2347,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey doston mein merey nazdik sab sey ziyada rashk karney key laaiq wo momin hai jo maal aur aulad sey halka phulka ho, namaz mein jisey rahat milti ho, apney rab ki ibadat achchhey dhang sey karney wala ho, aur khilwat (ekaant) mein bhi uska muteea' aur farma-bardar raha ho, logon key darmiyan aisi gumnaami ki zindagi guzar raha ho ke ungliyon sey uski taraf ishara nahin kiya jata, aur uska rizq ba-qadr « کفاف »zarurat ho phir bhi is par sabir rahey, phir aap ney apna haath zamin par maara aur farmaya : ''jaldi uski maut aaye taake is par roney waliyan thodi hon aur uski meeras kam ho.''"
2348,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kamiyab huwa wo shakhs jisney Islam qubul kya aur b-qadr zarurat  « كفاف » usey rozi hasil hui aur Allah ney usey (apney diye huye par) sabr karne wala « قانع » bana diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2349,unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''mubarak-baadi ho us shakhs ko jisey Islam ki hidayat mili aur usey b-qadr (paryapt) « کفاف » rozi mili phir wo usi par sabr karne wala aur mutmain raha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Haani ka naam Humed bin Haani hai.
2350,"eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! main aap sey mohabbat karta hun, aap ney farmaya : ''jo keh rahey ho uskey barey mein soch samajh lo.''  usney phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aap sey mohabbat karta hun, aap ney farmaya : ''jo keh rahey ho uskey barey mein soch samajh lo.'' , usney phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aap sey mohabbat karta hun, isi tarah teen dafa kaha to aap ney farmaya : ''agar tum mujh sey waqae mohabbat kartey ho to faqr (ghareebi) aur mohtaji ka taat tayyar rakho isliye ke jo shakhs mujhey dost banana chahta hai uski taraf faqr itni tezi sey jata hai ke itna tez sailab ka pani bhi apney bahaao key rukh par nahin jata.''"
2351,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''muhaajir fuqaraa jannat mein maaldaar Muhajir sey paanch sau saal pehley dakhil hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2352,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dua ki : « اللهم أحيني مسكينا وأمتني مسكينا واحشرني في زمرة المساكين يوم القيامة » ''ya-Allah ! mujhey miskini ki haalat mein zinda rakh aur miskini ki haalat mein wafat dey aur qiyamat key roz miskinon key khaney (زمرے) mein se utha.''  Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney daryaft iya Allah key Rasool ! aisa kyon ? aap ney farmaya : ''isliye ke miskin jannat mein maaldaro sey chaalis saal pehley dakhil hongey, lihaza aey Aaisha kisi bhi miskeen ko darwazey sey wapis na karo agar-che khajoor ka eik tukda hi sahi , Aaisha ! miskinon sey mohabbat karo aur un sey qurbat ikhtiyar karo, beshak Allah Taala tum ko roze qiyamat apney sey qarib kerega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
2353,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''fuqara jannat mein maaldaaron sey paanch so baras pehley dakhil hongey aur ye qiyamat key aadha din key barabar hoga'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2354,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''faqir o mohtaj musalman jannat mein maaldaaron sey aadha din pehley dakhil hongey aur ye aadha din paanch so baras key barabar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2355,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya : ''faqir o mohtaj musalman jannat mein maaldaaron sey chaalis saal pehley dakhil hongey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2356,"main ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to unhoney hamarey liye khana talab kya aur kaha ke main kisi khaney sey sair nahin hoti hun ke rona chahti hun phir roney lagti hun . mainey sawal kya : aisa kyon ? Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : main us haalat ko yad karti hun jis par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka intiqal huwa , Allah ki qism ! aap roti aur gosht sey eik din mein do baar kabhi sair nahin huye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2357,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do roz mutawatir jo ki roti kabhi sair ho kar nahin khai yahan tak ke aap wafat paa gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2358,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur aap key ehale-khana ney musalsal teen din tak gehun ki roti sair ho kar nahin khai yahan tak ke aap intiqal farma gaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2359,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar sey jo ki roti (ehale-khana ki) zarurat sey ziyada nahin hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Yahya bin abi Buker koofi hain, abu-Buker jo Yahya key walid hain Sufiyan Sory ney un ki hadees riwayat ki hai, 3- Yahya bin Abdullah bin Buker Misri hain aur Les key shagrid hain."
2360,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur aap key ghar waley musalsal kaee raaten khaali pet guzar detey, aur raat ka khana nahin paatey they. aur un ki aksar khurak jo ki roti hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2361,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye dua ki اللهم اجعل رزق آل محمد قوتا ''aey Allah ! Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar walon ko sirf utni rozi dey jis sey unkey jism ka rishta barqarar reh sakey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2362,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aaney waley kal key liye kuch nahin rakh chhodtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- ye hadees « an Jaafar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) an Sabit an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey mursalan bhi marvi hai."
2363,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chauki (ya mez) par khana kabhi nahin khaya aur na hi kabhi bareek aatey ki roti khai yahan tak ke duniya sey kooch kar gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Saeed bin abi Aruba ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2364,"un sey puchha gaya : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kabhi meda ki roti khai hai? Sehal ney jawab diya : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney meda ki roti dekhi bhi nahin yahan tak ke rihlat farma gaey. phir un sey puchha gaya : kya aap logon key paas ehade-nabawi mein chhalni thi? kaha hum logon key paas chhalni nahin thi. phir un sey puchha gaya ke aap log jo key aatey ko kaisey saaf kartey they? to kaha : pehley hum is mein phoonkein maartey they to jo udna hota wo ud jata tha phir hum is mein pani dal kar usey goondh letey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is hadees ko Malik bin Anas ney bhi abu-Haazim sey riwayat kya hai."
2365,"mein pehla shakhs hun jisney Allah ki raah mein khoon bahaaya (yani kafir ko qatl kya) aur main pehla shakhs hun jisney Allah ki raah mein teer phenka, mainey apney aap ko Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sathiyon ki eik jamaat key sath jihad kartey huye dekha hai, khaney key liye hum darakhton key pattey aur « habla » ( khaardaar darkht key phal ( key ilawa aur kuch nahin paatey they, yahan tak ke hum log bakriyon aur oonton ki tarah qazaey-hajat mein mengniyan nikaltey they, aur qabila bani Asad key log mujhey Deen key silsiley mein taan o tashnee kartey hain, agar main usi laaiq hon to bada hi mehroom hun aur merey tamam aamal zaya o barbad ho gaey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2366,"main Arab ka pehla shakhs hun jisney raahe-khuda mein teer phenka , aur hamney apney aap ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath jihad kartey waqt dekha hai ke hamarey paas khaardaar darakhton key phal aur keekar key darkht key ilawa khaney key liye kuch na tha yahan tak ke hum log qazaey-hajat mein bakriyon ki tarah mengniyan nikala kartey they, aur ab qabila bani-Asad key log mujhey Deen key silsiley mein malamat karney lagey hain, agar main isi laaiq hun to bada hi mehroom hun aur merey aamal zaya ho gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Utba bin ghazawaan sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2367,"hum Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein mojud they, aap key paas geru sey rangey huye do katan key kapdey they, unhoney eik kapdey mein naak ponchhin aur kaha : waah waah, abu-Huraira! katan mein naak ponchta hai, halanke eik wo zamana bhi tha ke main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney, aur hujra Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key darmiyan bhook ki shiddat ki wajeh sey behosh ho kar gir padta to koi aaney wala aata aur meri gardan par apna paaon rakh deta aur samajhta ke main pagal hun, halanke main pagal nahin hota tha aisa sirf bhook ki shiddat ki wajeh sey hota tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees aur is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2368,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab logon ko namaz padhatey to saf mein khadey bahut sey log bhook ki shiddat ki wajeh sey gir padtey they, ye log as-haab suffa they, yahan tak ke dehati log kehtey ke ye sab pagal aur majnun hain, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz sey farigh hotey to un ki taraf mutawajjeh hotey aur farmatey : agar tum logon ko Allah key nazdik apna martaba malum ho jaey to tum is sey kahin ziyada faqr o faaqa aur hajat ko pasand kartey'', Fazala (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main us waqt Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2369,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khilafe-mamool aisey waqt mein ghar sey nikley ke jab aap nahin nikaltey they aur na us waqt aap sey koi mulaqat karta tha, phir aap key paas abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) pahunchey to aap ney puchha : abu-Bakar tum yahan kaisey aaye ? unhoney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main isliye nikla taake aap sey mulaqat karun aur aap key chehrae-anwar ko dekhun aur aap par salam pesh karun, kuch waqfey key baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aap ney puchha : Umar! tum yahan kaisey aaye? is par unhoney bhook ki shikayat ki, aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey bhi kuch bhook lagi hai, phir sab mil kar Abul-Hesham bin Tahiyan Ansari key ghar pahunchey, unkey paas bahut ziyada khajoor key darkht aur bakriyan thin magar unka koi khaadim nahin tha, un logon ney Abul-Hesham ko ghar par nahin paya to unki biwi sey puchha : tumharey shohar kahan hain? usney jawab diya ke wo hamarey liye mitha pani laney gaey hain, guftgu ho rahi thi ke usi doran! Abul-Hesham eik bhari hui mashk liye aa pahunchey , unhoney mashk ko rakha aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey lipat gaey aur kaha : merey maa baap aap par fidaa hon , phir sab ko wo apney baagh mein ley gaey aur unkey liye eik bistar bichaya phir khajoor key darkht key paas gaey aur wahan sey khajuron ka guchchaa ley kar aaye aur usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney rakh diya . aap ney farmaya : '' hamarey liye is mein sey taza khajuron ko chun kar kyon nahin laye? arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey chaha ke aap khud un mein sey chun lein , ya ye kaha ke aap hazraat paki khajuron ko kachchi khajuron mein sey khud pasand kar lein, beharhal sab ney khajoor khai aur unkey us laye huye pani ko piya, uskey baad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai yaqinan ye un nematon mein sey hai jinkey barey mein qiyamat key din sawal kya jaeyga aur wo nematon ye hain : baagh ka thanda saya , paki hui umda khajuren aur thanda pani '' , phir Abul-Hesham uth khadey huye taake un logon key liye khana tayyar karen to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey kaha : '' doodh waley janwer ko zibeh na karna'', chunanche aap key hukm key mutabiq unhoney bakri ka eik mada bacha ya nar bacha zibeh kya aur usey pakka kar un hazraat key samney pesh kya, un sabhon ney usey khaya aur phir aap ney Abul-Hesham sey puchha ? kya tumharey paas koi ghulam hai? unhoney nahi mein jawab diya to aap ney farmaya : '' jab hamarey paas koi qaidi aaye to tum hum sey milna '' , phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas do qaidi laye gaey jinkey sath teesra nahin tha , Abul-Hesham bhi aaye to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey kaha ke un dono mein sey kisi eik ko pasand kar lo , unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap khud hamarey liye pasand kar diijiye. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' beshak jis sey mashwara liya jaey wo ameen hota hai. lihaza tum us ko ley lo (eik ghulam ki taraf ishara kartey huye ( kyonkey hamney isey namaz padhtey huye dekha hai aur is ghulam key sath achcha sulook karna '' , phir Abul-Hesham apni biwi key paas gaey aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baaton sey usey ba-khabar kya, unki biwi ney kaha ke tum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wasiyat ko pura na kar sakogey magar ye ke us ghulam ko azad kar do, isliye Abul-Hesham ney fauran usey azad kar diya, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney irshad farmaya : ''Allah taala ney kisi Nabi ya khalifa ko nahin bheja hai magar uskey sath do razdaar sathi hotey hain, eik usey bhalai ka hukm deta hai aur burai sey rokta hai, jabke doosra sathi usey kharab karney mein koi kasar utha nahin rakhta, pas jisey burey sathi sey bacha liya gaya goya wo badi aafat sey najat paa gaya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2370,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma ghar sey nikley , uskey baad Raavi ney mazkura hadees jaisi hadees bayan ki, lekin is mein Abu-Hurera ka zikr nahin kya, Sheban ki) sabiqa ( hadees abu awaana ki) us ( hadees sey ziyada mukammal aur ziyada taweel hai, Sheban muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa aur sahibe-kitab hain, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi marvi hai, aur ye hadees ibne-Abbas sey bhi marvi hai."
2371,"hamney (jange-khandaq key doran) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey bhook ki shikayat ki aur apney pet sey kapda uthaya jin par eik eik pathar bandhaa huwa tha so aap ney apney Mubarak pet sey kapda uthaya to is par do pathar bandhey huye they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2372,tum log jo chahtey ho khatey peetey ho halanke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko is haal mein dekha ke raddi khajuren bhi us miqdaar mein aap ko muyassar na thin jin sey aap apna pet bhartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2373,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maaldaari saaz o saman ki kasrat ka naam nahin hai, balke asal maaldari nafs ki maaldari hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2374,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : ''ye maal sarsabz aur mitha hai padhi. jisney usey halal tareeqey sey hasil kya uskey liye is mein barkat hogi aur kitney aisey hain jo Allah aur uskey Rasool key maal ko haram o najaaiz tariqa sey hasil karney waley hain unkey liye qiyamat key din jahannam ki aag tayyar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2375,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Dinar ka banda maloon hai, dirham ka banda maloon hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa « an abi Saleh an abi Hurera an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey marvi hai aur ye bhi sanad us sey ziyada mukammal aur taweel hai."
2376,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' do bhookey bhediye jinhen bakriyon key rewad mein chhod diya jaey itna nuqsan nahin pahunchaaeyngey jitna nuqsan aadmi key maal o jaah ki hirs uskey Deen ko pahunchati hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, aur wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain lekin iski sanad sahih nahin hai."
2377,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik chataai par so gaey, neend sey bedaar huye to aap key pehlu par chataai ka nishan pad gaya tha, Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! hum aap key liye eik bichona bana den to behtar hoga, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mujhey duniya sey kya matlab hai, meri aur duniya ki misal aisi hai jaisey eik sawar ho jo eik darkht key nichey saya hasil karney key liye bethey, phir wahan sey kooch kar jaey aur darkht ko usi jagah chhod dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2378,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi apney dost key Deen par hota hai, isliye tum mein sey har shakhs ko ye dekhna chahiye ke wo kis sey dosti kar raha hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2379,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''murdey key sath qabr tak teen cheezen jati hain, phir do cheezen lot aati hain aur sath main eik baqi reh jati hai, uskey rishtedaar, uska maal aur uskey aamal sath mein jatey hain phir rishtedaar, aur maal lot aatey hain aur sirf uska amal uskey sath baqi reh jata hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2380,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : '' kisi aadmi ney koi bartan apney pet sey ziyada bura nahin bhara, aadmi key liye chand luqmey hi kafi hain jo uski peeth ko sidha rakhen aur agar ziyada hi khana zaruri ho to pet ka eik tihai hissey apney khaney key liye, eik tihai pani peeney key liye aur eik tihai saans leney key liye baqi rakhey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2381,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo riyaakaari kerega to Allah Taala qiyamat key din usey logon key samney zahir kar dega , aur jo Allah ki ibadat shohrat key liye kerega to Allah Taala qiyamat key din usey ruswa aur zaleel kerega.''  farmaya : ''jo logon par reham nahin karta is par Allah Taala bhi reham nahin karta.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Jundub aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2382,"eik martaba wo Madina mein dakhil huye, achcha eik aadmi ko dekha jis key paas kuchh log jama they, unhoney puchha ke ye kon hain? logon ney jawaaban arz kiya : ye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hain, Shafiya Asbahi ka bayan hai ke main unkey qarib huwa yahan tak ke unkey samney beth gaya aur wo logon sey hadees bayan kar rahey they, jab wo hadees bayan kar chukey aur tanha reh gaey to mainey un sey kaha : main aap sey Allah ka baar-baar wasta dey kar poochh raha hun ke aap mujh sey aisi hadees bayan kijiye jisey aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna ho aur usey achchhi tarah jana aur samjha ho. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : theek hai, yaqinan main tum sey aisi hadees bayan karunga jisey mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bayan kiya hai aur mainey usey achchhi tarah jana aur samjha hai. phir Abu-Hurera ney zor ki cheekh maari aur behosh ho gaey, thodi der baad jab ifaaqa (faaida) huwa to farmaya : yaqinan main tum sey wo hadees bayan karunga jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey usi ghar mein bayan kiya tha jahan merey siwa koi nahin tha, phir dobara Abu-Hurera ney cheekh maari aur behosh ho gaey, phir jab ifaaqa (faaida) huwa to apney chehrey ko ponchha aur farmaya : zarur main tum sey wo hadees bayan karunga jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey bayan kiya hai aur us ghar mein merey aur aap key siwa koi nahin tha, phir Abu-Hurera ney zor ki cheekh maari aur behosh ho gaey, apney chehrey ko ponchh aur phir jab ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : zarur main tum sey wo hadees bayan karunga jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey bayan kiya hai aur us ghar mein merey aur aap key siwa koi nahin tha, phir Abu-Hurera ney zor ki cheekh maari aur behosh ho kar munh key bal zamin par gir padey, mainey badi der tak unhen apna sahara diye rakha phir jab ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey ye hadees bayan ki hai : ''qiyamat key din jab har ummat ghutnon key bal padi hogi to Allah Taala apney bandon key darmiyan faisley key liye nuzool farmaeyga, phir us waqt faisla key liye sab sey pehley aisey shakhs ko bulaya jaeyga jo Quran ka Hafiz hoga, doosra shaheed hoga aur teesra maaldaar hoga, Allah Taala haafize Quran sey kaheyga : kya mainey tujhey apney Rasool par nazil karda kitab ki taalim nahin di thi ? wo kaheyga : yaqinan aey merey rab ! Allah Taala farmaeyga jo ilm tujhey sikhaya gaya uskey mutabiq tu ney kya amal kiya? wo kaheyga : main us Quran key zariey raaton din teri ibadat karta tha, Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot kaha aur farishtey bhi us sey kahengey ki tu ney jhoot kaha , phir Allah Taala kaheyga : (Quran seekhney sey) tera maqsad ye tha ke log tujhey qaari kahen, so tujhey kaha gaya, phir sahabe maal ko pesh kiya jaeyga aur Allah Taala us sey puchheyga : kya mainey tujhey har chiz ki wusat na dey rakhi thi, yahan tak ke tujhey kisi ka mohtaj nahin rakha? wo arz kerega : yaqinan merey rab ! Allah Taala farmaeyga : mainey tujhey jo cheezen di thin is mein kya amal kiya ? wo kaheyga : sila rehmi karta tha aur sadqa aur khairat karta tha, Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot kaha aur farishtey bhi usey jhutlayengey, phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : balke tum ye chahtey they ke tumhen sakhi kaha jaey, so tumhen sakhi kaha gaya, uskey baad shaheed ko pesh kiya jaeyga, Allah Taala us sey puchheyga : tujhey kis liye qatl kiya gaya? wo arz kerega : mujhey teri raah mein jihad ka hukm diya gaya chunanche mainey jihad kiya yahan tak ke shaheed ho gaya, Allah Taala us sey kaheyga : tu ney jhoot kaha, farishtey bhi usey jhutlayengey, phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : tera maqsad ye tha ke tujhey bahaadur kaha jaey so tujhey kaha gaya.''  phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey zaanu par apna haath maar kar farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! yehi wo pehley teen shakhs hain jin sey qiyamat key din jahannam ki aag bhadkai jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Waleed abu-Usman kehtey hain : Aqba bin Muslim ney mujhey khabar di ke Shafiya Asbahi  ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar unhen is hadees sey ba-khabar kiya tha. abu-Usman kehtey hain : Alaa bin Abi Hakeem ney mujh sey bayan kiya ke wo Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key jallad they, phir Muawiya key paas eik aadmi pahuncha aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey is hadees sey unhen ba-khabar kiya to Muawiya ney kaha : un teeno key sath aisa maamla huwa to baqi logon key sath kya hoga, ye keh kar Muawiya zaar o qatar roney lagey yahan tak ke hamney samjha ke wo zinda nahin bachengey, aur hum logon ney yahan tak keh dala ke ye shakhs shar ley kar aaya hai, phir jab Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko ifaaqa huwa to unhoney apney chehrey ko saaf kiya aur farmaya : ''yaqeenan Allah aur uskey Rasool ney sach farmaya hai'' aur is aayate-karima ki tilawat ki :(من كان يريد الحياة الدنيا وزينتها نوف إليهم أعمالهم فيها وهم فيها لا يبخسون أولئك الذين ليس لهم في الآخرة إلا النار وحبط ما صنعوا فيها w batil ما كانوا يعملون) ''jo shakhs duniyaawi zindagi aur uski zeb aur zeenat ko chahega to hum duniya hi mein uskey aamal ka pura pura badla dey dengey aur koi kami nahin kerengey, ye wohi log hain jinka aakhirat mein jahannam key ilawa aur koi hissa nahin hai aur duniya key andar hi unkey sarey aamal zaya aur batil ho gaey.'' (Sura Hud :16). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2383,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(جب الحزن) ( gham ki wadi ( sey Allah Taala ki panah maango.''  Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! (جب الحزن) kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jahannam ki eik wadi hai jis sey jahannam bhi har roz sau martaba panah maangti hai.''  phir Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! is mein kon log dakhil hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''riyakar Quran ke Qaari (us mein dakhil hongey).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2384,"eik aadmi ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aadmi nek amal karta hai phir usey chhipata hai lekin jab logon ko uski ittilaa ho jati hai to wo usey pasand karta hai? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''uskey liye do ajr hain eik neki key chhipaaney ka aur doosra uskey zahir ho janey ka.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Aamash waghera ney is hadees ko «Habeeb bin Abi Sabit an Abi Saleh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam» ki sanad sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai, aur Aamash key shagirdon ney is mein « an abi Huraira » ka zikr nahin kiya. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki tafseer kartey huye farmaya : uskey nek amal key zahir ho janey par logon key pasand karney ka matlab ye hai ke logon ki tareef aur sanaa khair ko wo pasand karta hai isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai ke ''tum log zamin par Allah key gawah ho.'' yaqinan usey logon ki tareef pasand aati hai kyonkey usey logon ki tareef sey aakhirat key khair ki ummid hoti hai, albatta agar koi logon key jaan janey par isliye khush hota hai ke uskey nek amal ko jaan kar log uski tazeem aur takrim kerengey to ye riya aur dikhaawe mein dakhil ho jaeyga. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney iski tafseer ye ki hai ke logon key jaan janey par wo isliye khush hota hai ke nek amal mein log uski iqtida (pairvi) kerengey aur usey bhi unkey aamal mein ajr milega to ye khushi bhi munasib hai."
2385,"eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! qiyamat kab aayegi? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz padhney key liye khadey ho gaey, phir jab namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : ''qiyamat key barey mein sawal karney wala kahan hai?'' us aadmi ney kaha : main mojud hun Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key liye tum ney kya tayyari kar rakhi hai.''  usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey koi ziyada saum aur salaat (roza aur namaz) ikhatta nahin ki hai (yani nawaafil waghera) magar ye baat hai ke main Allah aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat karta hun, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi uskey sath hoga jis sey mohabbat karta hai, aur tum bhi isi key sath ho'ogey jis sey mohabbat kartey ho.'' Anas ka bayan hai ke Islam laney key baad mainey musalmanon ko itna khush hotey nahin dekha jitna aap key is qol sey wo sab khush nazar aa rahey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2386,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har aadmi isi key sath hoga jis sey wo mohabbat karta hai aur usey wohi badla milega jo kuchh usney kamaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan Basri ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, aur Hasan Basri ney Anas bin Malik sey aur Anas bin Malik Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Masood , Safwan bin Assaal, Abu-Hurera aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2387,"eik dehati jiski aawaz bahut bhari thi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Muhammad ! eik aadmi qom sey mohabbat karta hai albatta wo un sey amal mein peechhey hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi isi key sath hoga jis sey wo mohabbat karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2388,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main apney bandey key guman key mutabiq hun jaisa wo guman mujh sey rakhey, aur main uskey sath hun jab bhi wo mujhey pukarta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2389,eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey neki aur badi key barey mein sawal kiya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''neki achchhey akhlaq ka naam hai aur gunah wo hai jo tumharey dil mein khatak paida karey aur logon ka is par bakhabar hona hona tum par nagawar guzrey.''
2390,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''Allah Tabarak w taala ney farmaya : meri azmat aur buzurgi key liye aapas mein mohabbat karney walon key liye qiyamat key din Noor ( roshni ( key aisey member hongey jin par anbiya aur shuda bhi rashk karen.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Darda , ibne-Masood , Ubada bin Samit , Abu-Hurera aur abu Malik Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2391,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''saat qism key log aisey hain jinhen Allah Taala us din ke jab uskey ( arsh key ( saye key ilawa koi saya na hoga apney arsh key saye mein jagah dega : un mein sey eik insaf karney wala hukmaran hai, doosra wo nojawan hai jo Allah ki ibadat mein pala-badha padhi. , teesra wo shakhs hai jis ka dil masjid mein laga huwa ho,  chotha wo do aadmi jinhoney sirf Allah ki raza key liye eik doosrey key sath mohabbat ki usi key wastey jama hotey hain aur usi key wastey alag hotey hain, paanchwan wo aadmi jo tanhai mein Allah ka zikr karey aur azabe Ilaahi key khof mein aansu bahaaey, chhata wo aadmi jisey khoobsurat aurat gunah ki dawat dey, lekin wo kahey ke mujhey Allah ka khof hai, saatwaan wo aadmi jisney koi sadqa kiya to usey chhupaya yahan tak ke uskey baaein hath ko bhi na pata chaley ke daain haath ney kya kharch kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Imam Malik bin Anas sey iskey ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi isi key jaisi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, in mein bhi Raavi ney shak ka izhar kiya hai aur kaha hai « an abi Huraira Aw an abi Saeed » aur Ubedullah bin umr Umri ney is hadees ko Khubaib bin Abdur-Rehman sey baghair shak key riwayat kiya hai, is mein unhoney sirf « an abi Huraira » kaha hai."
2392,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi apney kisi musalman bhai sey mohabbat karey to wo apni us mohabbat sey aagah kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Miqdam ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
2393,"eik shakhs ney khadey ho kar eik ameer ki tareef shuru ki to Miqdaad bin Amr Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) uskey chehrey par mitti dalney lagey , aur kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein hukm diya hai ke tareef karney walon key munh mein mitti dal den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- zyada ney ye hadees Mujahid sey, Mujahid ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai halanke Mujahid ki riwayat jo Abu-Ma'mar sey hai wo ziyada sahih hai. 3- Abu-Ma'mar ka naam Abdullah bin Sakhbara hai aur Miqdaad bin Aswad Miqdaad bin Amr Al Kindi hain, jinki kunniyat abu Maabad hai. Aswad bin Abd Yaghus ki taraf un ki nisbat isliye ki gaee kyonkey unhoney Miqdaad ko ladakpan mein apna munh bola beta bana liya tha. 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2394,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein hukm diya ke hum be-ja tareef karney walon key munh mein mitti dal den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey gharib hai.
2395,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''momin key siwa kisi ki sohbat ikhtiyar na karo, aur tumhara khana sirf muttaqi hi khaye.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2396,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala apney kisi bandey key sath khair aur bhalai ka irada karta hai to usey duniya hi mein jald saza dey deta hai padhi. , aur jab apney kisi bandey key sath shar ( burai (ka irada karta hai to uskey gunahon ki saza ko rokey rakhta hai. yahan tak ke qiyamat key din usey puri puri saza deta hai.''"
2397,Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key dard sey ziyada dard kisi shakhs ka nahin dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2398,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! sab sey ziyada musibat kis par aati hai? aap ney farmaya : ''anbiya aur Rasool par , phir jo unkey baad martabe mein hain, phir jo unkey baad hain, bandey ki aazmaaish uskey Deen key mutabiq hoti hai, agar banda apney Deen mein sakht hai to uski musibat bhi sakht hoti hai aur agar wo apney Deen mein naram hota hai to uskey Deen key mutabiq musibat bhi hoti hai, phir musibat bandey key sath hamesha rehti hai, yahan tak ke banda roey zamin par is haal mein chalta hai ke is par koi gunah nahin hota.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. is baab mein Abu-Hurera aur Huzefa bin Yamaan ki behan Fatima (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sawal kiya gaya ke museebatein kis par ziyada aati hain? to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Anbiya aur Rasool par phir jo unkey baad martabe mein hain phir jo unkey baad main hon.''"
2399,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin mard aur momin aurat ki jaan, aulad, aur maal mein aazmaaishein aati rehti hain yahan tak ke jab wo marney key baad Allah sey mulaqat kartey hain to un par koi gunah nahin hota.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2400,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : jab main apney bandey ki piyari aankhen chheen leta hun to merey paas uska badla sirf jannat hi hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Arqam Raziallahu anhuma sey ahadees aai hain.
2401,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : mainey jiski piyari aankhen chhin lein aur usney is par sabr kiya aur sawab ki ummid rakhi to main usey jannat key siwa aur koi badla nahin dunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2402,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab qiyamat key din aisey logon ko sawab diya jaeyga jinki duniya mein aazmaaish hui thi to ehale-aafiyat khahish kerengey kaash! duniya mein unki khaalen qainchiyon sey katri jaatin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- baaz logon ney is hadees ka kuchh hissa (عن الأعمش an طلحة بن مصرف an مسروق)  ki sanad Masruq key qol sey riwayat kiya hai."
2403,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo bhi martaa hai wo naadim aur sharminda hota hai.''  Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! sharam aur nadaamat ki kya wajeh hai?'' aap ney farmaya : ''agar wo shakhs nek hai to usey is baat par nadaamat hoti hai ke wo ziyada sey ziyada neki na kar saka, aur agar wo bad hai to naadim hota hai ke mainey badi sey apney aap ko nikala kyon nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Yahya bin Ubedullah key barey mein Shoba ney kalam kiya hai, aur ye Yahya bin Ubedullah bin Mohab Madni hain."
2404,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aakhir zamaney mein kuchh aisey log niklengey jo Deen key sath duniya key bhi talab-gaar hongey, wo logon ko apni saadgi aur narmi dikhaney key liye bhaid ki khaal pahneingey, un ki zabanen shukr sey bhi ziyada meethi hongi jabke unkey dil bhadiyon key dil ki tarah hongey. Allah Taala farmata hai : kya ye log mujh par ghurur kartey hain ya mujh par jur'at kartey hain main apni zaat ki qism khata hun ke zarur main un par aisa fitna nazil karunga jis sey un mein ka aqlmand aadmi bhi hairaan reh jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2405,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : mainey eik aisi makhluq paida ki hai jinki zabanen shehad sey bhi ziyada meethi hain aur unkey dil eilwa key phal sey bhi ziyada kadwe hain, main apni zaat ki qism khata hun ! ke zarur main unkey darmiyan aisa fitna nazil karunga jis sey un mein ka aqlmand aadmi bhi hairaan reh jaaeyga, phir bhi ye mujh par ghurur kartey hain ya jur'at kartey hain?'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2406,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! najat ki kiya surat hai? aap ney farmaya : ''apni zaban ko qabu mein rakho, apney ghar ki wusat mein muqayyad raho aur apni khataaon par rotey raho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2407,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''insan jab subah karta hai to uskey sarey aaza zaban key samney apni aajizi ka izhar kartey hain aur kehtey hain : to hamarey silsiley mein Allah sey dar isliye ke hum terey sath hain agar to sidhi rahi to hum sab sidhey rahengey aur agar to tedhi ho gaee to hum sab bhi tedhey ho jaeyngey.''
2408,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo mujh sey apni dono daadhon aur dono taangon key bech ka zaamin ho main uskey liye jannat ka zaamin hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Sehal bin Saad ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
2409,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey Allah ney uski taangon aur daadhon key darmiyan ki chiz key shar aur fasad sey bacha liya wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat karney waley Raavi Abu-Haazim ka naam Salman hai. ye Aza Ashjaiyya key azad karda ghulam hain aur koofi hain aur Sehal bin Saad sey riwayat karney waley Raavi Abu-Haazim ka naam Salma bin Dinar hai jo Zaahid Madni hain.
2410,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujh sey aisi baat bayan farmaain jisey main mazbooti sey pakad lun, aap ney farmaya : ''kaho : mera rab (maboode-haqeeqi) Allah hai, phir isi ehad par qaaim raho.'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ko mujh sey kis chiz ka ziyada khof hai? aap ney apni zaban pakdi aur farmaya : ''isi ka ziyada khof hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Sufiyan bin Abdullah Saqafi sey kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2411,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zikre-Ilaahii key siwa kasrate kalam sey perhez karo isliye ke zikre Ilahi key siwa kasrate kalam dil ko sakht bana deta hai aur logon mein Allah sey sab sey ziyada door sakht dil wala hoga.''
2412,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''insan ki sari baaten uskey liye wabal hain un mein sey usey Amr bil Maaroof, nahi Anil-munkar aur zikre Ilaahi key siwa usey kisi aur ka sawab nahin milega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai isey hum sirf Muhammad bin Yazeed bin Khunais ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2413,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Salman aur Abu-Darda key maa-bain bhai chaara karwaya to eik din Salman ney Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki ziyaarat ki, dekha ke un ki biwi Umme Darda maamuli kapdo mein malboos (pehne hue) hain, chunanche unhoney puchha ke tumhari is haalat ki kya wajeh hai? unki biwi ney jawab diya : tumharey bhai Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko duniya sey koi raghbat nahin hai ke jab Abu-Darda ghar aaye to pehley unhoney Salman (Raziallahu anhu) key samney khana pesh kiya aur kaha : khaao mein aaj rozey sey hun. Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main nahin khaaunga yahan tak ke tum bhi merey sath khaao. chunanche Salman ney bhi khaya. phir jab raat aai to Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) tahajjud padhney key liye khadey ho gaey, to Salman ney un sey kaha : sau jaao wo sau gaey. phir tahajjud padhney key liye khadey huye to kaha sau jaao, chunanche wo so gaey, phir jab subah qarib hui to Salman ney un sey kaha : ab uth jaao chunanche dono ney uth kar namaz padhi. phir Salman ney un sey kaha : ''tumharey jism ka bhi tum par haq hai, tumharey rab ka tum par haq hai, tumharey mehman ka tum par haq hai, tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai, isliye har sahibe haq ko uska haq ada karo.''  iskey baad dono Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur aap sey us guftgu ka tazkira kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''Salman ney sach kaha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2414,un sey Madina key eik shakhs ney bayan kiya : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas eik khat likha ke mujhey eik khat likhye aur is mein kuchh wasiyat kijiye lekin bahut zyada nahin. chunanche Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas khat likha : dua aur salam key baad malum ho ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : ''jo logon ki narazagi mein Allah Taala ki raza ka Talib ho to logon sey pahunchney wali takleef key silsiley mein Allah uskey liye kafi hoga aur jo Allah ki narazagi mein logon ki raza ka Talib ho to Allah Taala unhin logon ko usey takleef deney key liye muqarrar kar dega.''  (والسلام علیک ''tum par Allah ki salamti nazil ho'') padhi. .
